content: संपन्न {%<ab>p. p.</ab>%} {@--1@} Prosperous, thriving, rich. {@--2@} Fortunate, successful, happy. {@--3@} Effected, brought about, accomplished. {@--4@} Finished, completed. {@--5@} Perfect. {@--6@} Full-grown, mature. {@--7@} Procured, obtained. {@--8@} Right, correct. {@--9@} Endowed with, possessed of. {@--10@} Turned out, become; ईदृशः संपन्नः <ls>U. 3.</ls> {@--11@} Perfectly acquainted or conversant with. --न्नः An epithet of Śiva. --न्नं {@--1@} Riches, wealth; <ls>Pt. 4. 115.</ls> {@--2@} A dainty, delicacy.
